<subSubSection pageId="12" pageNumber="511" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1436,1237,1334]" pageId="12" pageNumber="511">
First reported from 
<collectingCountry box="[370,436,1237,1262]" name="Malta" pageId="12" pageNumber="511">Malta</collectingCountry>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Leonardi, G." box="[477,663,1237,1262]" pageId="12" pageNumber="511" refId="ref17830" refString="Leonardi, G. (1920) Monografia delle Cocciniglie Italiane. Opera Postuma. Edizione curata e accresciuta di un'appendice dal Prof. F. Silvestri, Portici, vii + 555 pp. [in Italian]" type="book" year="1920">Leonardi (1920)</bibRefCitation>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="Borg, J." box="[674,811,1237,1262]" pageId="12" pageNumber="511" refId="ref16594" refString="Borg, J. (1932) Scale Insects of the Maltese Islands. Government Printing Office, Malta, 20 pp." type="book" year="1932">Borg (1932)</bibRefCitation>
recorded this species as found “here and there; on olive trees at Boschetto, San Antonio, Vallone 
<collectingRegion box="[636,676,1273,1298]" country="Malta" name="Lija" pageId="12" pageNumber="511">Lia</collectingRegion>
, Notabile, etc”. It was recorded again by 
<bibRefCitation author="Saliba, L. J." box="[1172,1328,1273,1298]" pageId="12" pageNumber="511" refId="ref19180" refString="Saliba, L. J. (1963) Insect pests of crop plants in the Maltese Islands. Department of Information, Malta, 35 pp." type="book" year="1963">Saliba (1963)</bibRefCitation>
as being occasionally found on olives, also by 
<bibRefCitation author="Haber, G. &amp; Mifsud, D." box="[573,840,1309,1334]" pageId="12" pageNumber="511" pagination="143 - 161" refId="ref17225" refString="Haber, G. &amp; Mifsud, D. (2007) Pests and diseases associated with olive trees in the Maltese Islands (Central Mediterranean). The Central Mediterranean Naturalist, 4 (3), 143 - 161." type="journal article" year="2007">Haber &amp; Mifsud (2007)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Mifsud, D. &amp; Falzon, A. &amp; Malumphy, C. &amp; De Lillo, E. &amp; Volvas, N. &amp; Porcelli, F." box="[894,1123,1309,1334]" pageId="12" pageNumber="511" pagination="5 - 34" refId="ref18516" refString="Mifsud, D., Falzon, A., Malumphy, C., De Lillo, E., Volvas, N. &amp; Porcelli, F. (2012) On some arthropods associated with Ficus species (Moraceae) in the Maltese Islands. Bulletin of the Entomological Society of Malta, 5, 5 - 34." type="journal article" year="2012">
Mifsud 
<emphasis box="[982,1038,1309,1334]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="511">et al.</emphasis>
(2012)
</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
